description: RCMW Group, Inc. engages in the production, branding, and marketing of consumer products in the United States and Canada. It offers non-nicotine vaporizer hardware and related batteries for cannabinoid marketplace; and hemp seed-based pet specialty supplements and products. The company was formerly known as Hemp Technology Inc. and changed its name to RCMW Group, Inc. in February 2021. RCMW Group, Inc. is based in Cheyenne, Wyoming.
